Rather late comment but for those who still has the problem with missing stylesheets, do this -

1) Download your theme
2) Extract the folder to your desktop
3) Find the folder the contains just the theme files
4) Move this folder to your wp-installation at wp-content/themes (via FTP) (Or create a zip file of that folder and then use the wordpress installation function)
